    <h1>Quick Guide: Using the bioRxiv Plugin with ChatGPT</h1>

    <img src="https://ed3cc36e4da8918fbfe790aa5b09beb3.auth.portal-pluginlab.ai/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffirebasestorage.googleapis.com%2Fv0%2Fb%2Fpluginlab.appspot.com%2Fo%2Fpublic%252Fplugins%252Fed3cc36e4da8918fbfe790aa5b09beb3%252Flogo%3Falt%3Dmedia%26token%3Dc303c882-3c34-4ac8-86be-b22db388f254&w=1920&q=75" alt="bioRxiv Plugin Logo">

    <h2>Introduction:</h2>
    <p>The bioRxiv plugin allows ChatGPT users to quickly fetch research papers from bioRxiv directly within the chat interface. Here's how to use it:</p>

    <h2>Steps:</h2>
    <h3>1. Activate the Plugin:</h3>
    <p>Ensure the bioRxiv plugin is installed and activated for your ChatGPT.</p>

    <h3>2. Fetching Papers:</h3>
    <p>To fetch a paper, simply type your request in the ChatGPT interface. Examples:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>"Get a research paper on molecules from bioRxiv."</li>
        <li>"Find me a bioRxiv paper on sharks."</li>
        <li>"Show nuclear fusion research papers from bioRxiv after 2022."</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Navigating Results:</h3>
    <p>ChatGPT will display a list of relevant papers based on your query.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Click on any title to view more details.</li>
        <li>If you wish to see more results or navigate to a different page of results, use commands like:</li>
        <ul>
            <li>"Show me page 3 of results."</li>
            <li>"Get more results."</li>
        </ul>
    </ul>

    <h2>Conclusion:</h2>
    <p>The bioRxiv plugin for ChatGPT simplifies the process of finding research papers by allowing you to search and navigate results directly within the chat. Use specific commands to refine and navigate your search results. Happy researching!</p>

